high_descs: Turn left towards the table with the pan.
Pick up the lettuce from the table.
Turn right towards the sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink and wash.
Walk towards the black table to the left.
Place the lettuce on to the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the clean lettuce on the black table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the lettuce.
Turn around and veer left to the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and pick it back up.
Step left a couple steps until you're in front of the black table.
Set the lettuce on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed head of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the white table.
Pick up the head of lettuce on the table behind the tomato
Turn right, and walk towards the sink
Place the lettuce in the sink, turn on the faucet to fill the sink with water, turn off the faucet, and retrieve the lettuce from the sink
Turn left and walk towards the small black table with three shelves.
Place the head of lettuce on the top shelf of the small black table
anns.task_desc: Find the head of lettuce, wash it, then place it on a small black table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the small table then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the head of lettuce that's in front of you.
Turn around and take a step the turn left and walk to the sink.
Wash the head of lettuce in the sink then pick it back up.
Take two steps left to face the small black table.
Put the clean head of lettuce on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce on the table.

high_descs: turn left, walk to the table
grab the cabbage on the table
turn around, walk to the sink on the left
put the cabbage in the sink, wash the cabbage with water, take the cabbage out
turn around, and walk around to the shelf in the corner
put the cabbage on the shelf
anns.task_desc: wash the cabbage in the sink, put the cabbage on the shelf

high_descs: Move to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the head of lettuce.
Turn around and walk to sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and then pick it back up.
Stand in front of the black shelves to the left of the sink.
Place the lettuce atop the black shelves.
anns.task_desc: Wash a head of lettuce in the sink.
